2025-07-09 16:45:05.611 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (7ms) [Parameters=[@__key_0='?' (DbType = Guid)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT m0."Id", m0."Email", m0."IsDeleted", m0."Name", p."Id", p."CreatedByEmail", p."Description", p."EndDate", p."IsDeleted", p."PoleFileId", p."StartDate", p."Title"
FROM (
    SELECT m."Id", m."Email", m."IsDeleted", m."Name"
    FROM "Moderators" AS m
    WHERE m."Id" = @__key_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS m0
